<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Universal_health_care&amp;action=edit&amp;section=36" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.1payer.net/" class="external text" title="http://www.1payer.net/" rel="nofollow">1payer.net</a>. Citizen action site for single-payer universal healthcare.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.healthrevolutionpetition.org/citizensincharge.html" class="external text" title="http://www.healthrevolutionpetition.org/citizensincharge.html" rel="nofollow">Health Revolution Petition Website</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.healthcare-now.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.healthcare-now.org/" rel="nofollow">Healthcare-NOW!</a>. A nonprofit advocacy group for single-payer universal healthcare.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pdamerica.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.pdamerica.org/" rel="nofollow">Progressive Democrats of America</a>, Democrats who support single-payer universal healthcare.</li>
<li><a href="http://republicansforsinglepayer.com/" class="external text" title="http://republicansforsinglepayer.com/" rel="nofollow">Republicans for Single-Payer Universal Healthcare</a> Republicans who support single-payer healthcare.</li>
<li><a href="http://singlepayeraction.org/" class="external text" title="http://singlepayeraction.org/" rel="nofollow">Single Payer Action</a>. Activist organization supporting single-payer universal healthcare.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.universalhealthct.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.universalhealthct.org/" rel="nofollow">Universal Health Care Foundation of Connecticut</a></li>
</ul>


